{"word":"G141 - αἱρετικός - hairetikós - hahee-ret-ee-kos' - Heretic","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἱρετικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hairetikós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hahee-ret-ee-kos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heretic"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வேதப்புரட்டன் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. fitted or able to take or choose a thing"},{"paragraph":"2. schismatic, factious, a follower of false doctrine"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/G140 - αἱρετίζω - hairetízō - hahee-ret-id'-zo/140\">G140</a>; a <i>schismatic</i>. (&ldquo;heretic&rdquo; is the Greek word itself.): - heretic [the Greekord itself]."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1243 - διαίρεσις - diaíresis - dee-ah'-ee-res-is/1243\">G1243</a>, <a href=\"#/G1244 - διαιρέω - diairéō - dee-ahee-reh'-o/1244\">G1244</a>, <a href=\"#/G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee/138\">G138</a>, <a href=\"#/G139 - αἵρεσις - haíresis - hah'-ee-res-is/139\">G139</a>, <a href=\"#/G140 - αἱρετίζω - hairetízō - hahee-ret-id'-zo/140\">G140</a>, <a href=\"#/G141 - αἱρετικός - hairetikós - hahee-ret-ee-kos'/141\">G141</a>"}]}